hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: VALUE
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: Get a previous job variable-value-of : "VALUE",Value is in ${VALUE}; Do not set default value;

hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: STATUS_NUM
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: Get a previous job variable-value-of : "STATUS_NUM",Value is in ${STATUS_NUM}; Do not set default value;

hudson.tasks.Shell.command:
#!/bin/bash set -e
GIT_EMAIL="tommylike@gmail.com" IMAGE_VERSION=$(git rev-parse HEAD) PROJECT_NAME="mindspore-test-website"
cd $WORKSPACE if [ ! -e ./success.txt ] then touch ./value.txt fi if [ ! -e ./faild.txt ] then touch ./faild.txt fi if [ -z `cat ./success.txt` ] then echo "0" > ./success.txt fi if [ -z `cat ./faild.txt` ] then echo "1" > ./falid.txt fi if [ "$STATUS_NUM" = "0" ] then echo $VALUE > ./success.txt fi if [ "$STATUS_NUM" = "1" ] then echo $VALUE > ./faild.txt fi if [ ${IMAGE_VERSION} = `cat ./success.txt` ] then echo "#############################################" echo "gitee registry files not change-01,excuted exit" echo "#############################################" exit 1 fi if [ `cat ./faild.txt` = `cat ./success.txt` ] && [ ${IMAGE_VERSION} = `cat ./faild.txt` ] then echo "#############################################" echo "gitee registry files not change-02,excuted exit" echo "#############################################" exit 1 fi
echo "正在执行任务构建................................."
